'''天主教利梅拉教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Limeirensis}}；{{lang-pt|Diocese de Limeira}}）是[[巴西|巴西]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]][[教區|教區]]，屬[[天主教坎皮納斯總教區|坎皮納斯總教區]]。

教區成立於1976年4月29日，<ref>{{cite journal|journal=[[宗座公報|宗座公報]]|publisher=梵蒂岡出版社|date=1976年|volume=68|title=''De superna animarum''|page=396|url=http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2068%20%5B1976%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|access-date=2014-01-02|archive-date=2010-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327070115/http://www.vatican.va/archive/aas/documents/AAS%2068%20%5B1976%5D%20-%20ocr.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>包括[[聖保羅州|聖保羅州]]東部十六市。2004年有教友632,706人（佔轄區總人口66.7%）、五十三個堂區、八十三名司鐸。

現任教區主教為{{link-pt|若瑟·羅勃·福爾特斯-帕勞|José Roberto Fortes Palau}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 20.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/20/191120d.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191120130940/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/20/191120d.html |archivedate=2019-11-20 |language=en |date=2019-11-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[宗座署理|宗座署理]]為{{link-en|羅蘭·布蘭德斯|Orlando Brandes}}<ref name="Vatican20190517">{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 17.05.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/17/190517c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190814130114/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/05/17/190517c.html |archivedate=2019-08-14 |language=en |date=2019-05-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休主教為{{link-en|威爾遜·迪亞斯-德奧利韋拉|Vilson Dias de Oliveira}}。<ref name="Vatican20190517" />

